    <p>If you want to learn about Vancouver bicycling activism and activism in general and how it’s a long game full of amazing folks then please buy or borrow from the library (it’s at VPL!):  <a href="https://www.vanbikes.ca/">Vanbikes</a>: Vancouver’s Bicycle People &amp; the Fight for Transportation Change, 1986-2011 by Colin Stein! Highly recommended! <a href="https://www.vanbikes.ca/store">Order the book at Colin’s site</a> if you have the $. $25 for the PDF, $50 for the book. I have a copy (and Barb and I are on page 310 :-), see if you can spot us!)</p>
